name: RBC Target 2025 U.S. Corporate Bond ETF
longDescription: Fund achieve its objective investing primarily in a portfolio of investment grade fixed-income securities issued in the U.S. market by U.S. and foreign corporations that mature in the same calendar year as the ETFs termination date. It is anticipated that the ETF will terminate on or about September 30, 2025.
fulldescription: Fund achieve its objective investing primarily in a portfolio of investment grade fixed-income securities issued in the U.S. market by U.S. and foreign corporations that mature in the same calendar year as the ETFs termination date. It is anticipated that the ETF will terminate on or about September 30, 2025. The investment objective of the ETF is to provide income, for a limited period of time ending on the ETFs termination date
